title: Counted By The Creator | Joel Osteen

description:
You are not limited by your past or by anyone's opinion. God counts you worthy, and He's already equipped you with everything you need to fulfill your destiny.

 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
